        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 2. Gyponana mali DeLong, 1942, male (voucher I02/19). A – dorsal view; B – lateral view; C – pygofer, valve, subgenital plate, and aedeagus, lateral view; D – pygofer, valve, subgenital plate, and aedeagus, dorsal view; E – styles, connective, and aedeagus, lateral view; F – styles, connective, and aedeagus, dorsal view; G – aedeagus, ventral view. Scale bar 1.0 mm." ;
